也許因為{{Math_pi}}的公式很簡短而且四處可見， {{Math_pi}}比其他數學常数在流行文化中更常見{{NoteTag|例如，柯利弗德·皮寇弗稱{{pi}}為「最知名的數學常数」，皮特森則寫道：「在所有數學常數當中，{{pi}}一向最受瞩目。」例如[[紀梵希|紀梵希]]{{pi}}香水、[[Π_(電影)|Π (電影)]]以及[[圓周率日|圓周率日]]。<ref>{{Citation |last=Pickover |first=Clifford A. |title=Keys to Infinity |year=1995 |page=59 |publisher=Wiley & Sons |isbn=9780471118572}}</ref><ref>{{Citation |last=Peterson |first=Ivars |title=Mathematical Treks: From Surreal Numbers to Magic Circles |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4gWSAraVhtAC&pg=PA17 |year=2002 |series=MAA spectrum |page=17 |publisher=Mathematical Association of America |isbn=9780883855379 |access-date=2017-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170201053727/https://books.google.com/books?id=4gWSAraVhtAC&pg=PA17 |archive-date=2017-02-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}。

