在1958年，{{tsl|en|Albert Eagle|阿尔伯特·伊格尔|阿尔伯特·伊格尔}}[[轉_(角)|提议]]将{{Math_pi}}换成[[Τ|{{tau}}（tau）]]以便简化公式。<math>\tau</math>在此定义为{{Math_pi}}的兩倍<ref name="AE1958">{{Cite book |title=The Elliptic Functions as They Should be: An Account, with Applications, of the Functions in a New Canonical Form |last=Eagle |first=Albert |publisher=Galloway and Porter, Ltd. |year=1958 |page=ix}}</ref>。然而，没有任何其他作者曾这样使用过<math>\tau</math>。有些人使用一个不同的值，<math>\tau=6.283185\ldots=2\pi</math>。<ref>Sequence {{OEIS2C|A019692}}</ref>这些人辩称<math>\tau</math>，不论是作为弧度制下一个圆形周长的1[[轉_(角)|转]]，还是作为弧长与半径的比值（而不是与直径的比值），都比{{Math_pi}}显得更加自然，也能因此简化掉许多公式。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=My Conversion to Tauism |url=http://www.maa.org/sites/default/files/pdf/Mathhorizons/apr12_aftermath.pdf |last=Abbott |first=Stephen |date=2012-04 |journal=Math Horizons |issue=4 |doi=10.4169/mathhorizons.19.4.34 |volume=19 |page=34 |ref=harv |access-date=2016-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928095819/http://www.maa.org/sites/default/files/pdf/Mathhorizons/apr12_aftermath.pdf |archive-date=2013-09-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |title=π Is Wrong! |url=http://www.math.utah.edu/~palais/pi.pdf |last=Palais |first=Robert |journal=The Mathematical Intelligencer |issue=3 |doi=10.1007/BF03026846 |year=2001 |volume=23 |pages=7–8 |ref=harv |access-date=2016-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080229083141/http://www.math.utah.edu/~palais/pi.pdf |archive-date=2008-02-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>已经有媒体报道称，有人在6月28日庆祝“<math>\tau</math>节”，并吃“两个派”，因为<math>\tau</math>的值大小约为6.28。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Tau Day: Why you should eat twice the pie |url=http://lightyears.blogs.cnn.com/2012/06/28/tau-day-why-you-should-eat-twice-the-pie/ |accessdate=2012-06-28 |date=2012-06-28 |work=Light Years - CNN |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130112211136/http://lightyears.blogs.cnn.com/2012/06/28/tau-day-why-you-should-eat-twice-the-pie/ |archive-date=2013-01-12 }}</ref>然而，对于<math>\tau</math>的使用还并没有在数学界成为主流。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Life of pi in no danger – Experts cold-shoulder campaign to replace with tau |url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1110630/jsp/nation/story_14178997.jsp |date=2011-06-30 |journal=Telegraph India |access-date=2016-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130713084345/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1110630/jsp/nation/story_14178997.jsp |archive-date=2013-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在1897年，一个业余的美国数学家试图通过[[印第安纳州议会|印第安纳州议会]]来通过後世所謂[[印第安纳圆周率法案|印第安纳圆周率法案]]的法案。这一法案因试图以法律命令强制规定一个数学常数而臭名远扬。该法案描述了一个[[化圆为方|化圆为方]]的方法，并间接提到了{{Math_pi}}的错误值，例如3.2。该法案通过了印第安纳州众议院的表决，但是被参议院否决。<ref name="Arndt" />{{rp|211–212}}<ref>{{harvnb|Posamentier|Lehmann|2004|pp=36–37}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |title=Indiana's squared circle |first=Arthur |date=1977-03 |journal=Mathematics Magazine |issue=3 |doi=10.2307/2689499 |volume=50 |pages=136–140 |jstor=2689499 |ref=harv |last1=Hallerberg}}</ref>

